
# Fake job offer

## Initiation
reach out over email

## Process
They tell you about some simple job for earning money with a salary like Rs 10k. 

They share proof of payment to others. 

They ask you to pay Rs 2k as a refundable deposit. 

When you start on the work they give you and submit, like a typing job, they decline it and ask you for more money with some reason.


## Mechanism
Job is fake. Proof of payment is fake. Any and all credentials are fake. 

## Best practices to prevent the fraud
Be aware of any job positing which ask you for money for any reason.         
